THIRD-PARTY FILTER LISTS

ShieldBrowse uses community-maintained filter lists under their respective licenses:

- EasyList / EasyPrivacy — GPL v3 (https://easylist.to)
- Peter Lowe's Ad Server List — McRae GPL (https://pgl.yoyo.org/adservers/)
- uBlock Origin Filters — GPL v3 (https://github.com/uBlockOrigin/uAssets)
- AdGuard Filters — GPL v3 (https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters)
- Fanboy's Lists — (https://fanboy.co.nz)
- URLhaus Malware Filter — (https://gitlab.com/malware-filter/urlhaus-filter)

These filter lists are fetched at runtime and used as data (blocking rule definitions).
They are not bundled in the extension source code.
